12.1.11--15 Rūpaanabhisamayādisuttapañcaka
Vacchagottasaṃyutta
Vacchagottavagga
Rūpaanabhisamayādisuttapañcaka
617--621.
1248Sāvatthinidānaṃ. “Rūpe kho, vaccha, anabhisamayā…pe…  rūpanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya anabhisamayā…pe… .
1249Sāvatthinidānaṃ. “Vedanāya kho, vaccha, anabhisamayā…pe… .
1250Sāvatthinidānaṃ. “Saññāya kho, vaccha, anabhisamayā…pe… .
1251Sāvatthinidānaṃ. “Saṅkhāresu kho, vaccha, anabhisamayā…pe… .
1252Sāvatthinidānaṃ. “Viññāṇe kho, vaccha, anabhisamayā…pe… .
1253Pannarasamaṃ.
